Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
1111 Cromwell Avenue located within Rocky Hill’s Compass Point Professional Park, a six-building, 66,000 SF office park situated on 8.4 acres. Conveniently located on Route 3, just off Interstate 91 via Exit 23, the property offers excellent highway access and visibility. 
 
Each of the buildings have their own private entrances to suites and very minimum common areas. Interior areas are well appointed with high-end finishes throughout and an ideal configuration for medical and office users. Ownership is offering competitive tenant improvement allowances for new tenants.
